Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:05.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do your laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, I'm opening the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opening the door, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:33.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep in a boy's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:36.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kanda-kun? \NI need to scold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:37.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:39.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I just asked you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:48.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When you've finished eating \Nthat, we'll do your laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:52.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you \Nto be sleeping in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for letting \NShiina-san sleep in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,H-How about you, Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.71,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get any sleep afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:16.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kanda-kun, aren't you \Nbusy writing your pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be sleeping in your bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:22.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm making \Ngood progress on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.43,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you haven't\N taken the cap off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:36.61,Saku-main,AOYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:41.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.57,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san must prefer Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:59.49,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm the one on Mashiro Duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:35.94,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,#06 The Blue After the Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.52,Saku-main,TRAINEE C,0000,0000,0000,,"But, O, what damned \Nminutes tells he o'er,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.94,Sign,SIGN (left),0000,0000,0000,,{\a4}Midterm Presentation: August 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.94,Sign,SIGN (right),0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}William \NShakespeare's\N Othello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.15,Saku-main,TRAINEE C,0000,0000,0000,,Who dotes, yet doubts, \Nsuspects, yet strongly loves!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:43.02,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,The presentation's coming up. \NI'm starting to get butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.12,Saku-main,TRAINEE B,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko, you've been practicing a lot, \Nso it should be a cinch for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.81,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,But who knows what'll happen \Nin the actual presentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:53.17,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll be happy as \Nlong as we can have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.61,Saku-main,TRAINEE B,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.73,Saku-main,TRAINEE B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanami, have you \Ngot your lines down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.40,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yeah... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.66,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.93,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work hard so that \Nour whole group passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.59,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:19.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home! I did a little \Nshopping and ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're having omelet rice tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You think omelet rice is easy, Nanamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.74,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Your womanly charm level must \Nrank as high as the Himalayas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get kouhai-kun and Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job, so I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.92,Saku-main,NAMAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, dinner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this when her magazine goes on sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same day as my presentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:57.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not far off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, I fixed your button.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Can you put out your laundry, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"O, beware, my lord, of jealousy;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It is the green-eyed monster \Nwhich doth mock—"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"Which doth mock the meat it feeds on."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami's on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.95,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Stressed because you haven't \Nhit your chick magnet phase yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:47.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.82,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's an urban legend anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I just said no—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?!\N I really believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's more an issue of whether \Nyou realize it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Jin-san, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.99,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.58,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did she confess her feelings to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you enjoy teasing me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Worried isn't the right word...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama's smart, and she's better than...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the average person at most things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she should stop \Ntrying to do it all herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're all living under the same roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think we should \Nhelp each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.68,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally different from \Nmy impression of Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But Aoyama-san must have her own\Nfeelings on the matter too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's found her goal, and had to \Nface her parents' opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's been alone since she left home,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so she probably thinks \Nshe needs to handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,everything by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's Mashiro-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.18,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She has to come to terms with that herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to leave her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.59,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you'd do, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking is good for you, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.19,Sign,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka Art Colleges
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.82,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to Suimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to an art school in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? What about Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.14,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything to Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.25,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.35,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.51,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Just act like you never found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:47.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to act around \NMisaki-senpai anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Jin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "how to act"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Only for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean... I was talking \Nto him about my pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even mention \Nyou for a millisecond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,M-Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:25.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I need to \Ndo to make Jin look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.77,Sign,DOC,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game!" Pitch\NTrain Train (Temp.): Original Train Puzzle Game\NDownloadable Mobile Phone Content\NEntry No. 780411: Kanda Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:32.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what do you want from Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that lovers do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.60,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to walk hand in hand with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:47.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:51.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,How does everyone else manage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're cute, so you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna play some \Ngames to cheer up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.16,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,To pick a fight with me... \NYou've grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, let's play a lot during \Nthe rest of summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,For me and Jin, it'll be \Nour last summer together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.76,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.06,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.36,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I just tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.96,Sign,CALENDAR,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Mashiron's \NMagazine \NOn Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.96,Sign,CALENDAR,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Nanamin's \NMidterm \NPresentation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:06.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! 10, 9, 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.04,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Your entry has been submitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:25.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! Mashiron, what's \Nwrong with Nanamin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.23,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.07,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoyama! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.92,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew working so hard would \Ncatch up with her eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't her presentation at \Nher training school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:07.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She probably tried to leave \Nearly so we wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she intended to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But, Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If Nanami wants to go, let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:35.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami worked hard. \NShe stayed up late every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.45,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure are loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.47,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.67,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.82,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.04,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.92,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're going out with this fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.21,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.34,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.51,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room and—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The taxi's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:32.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:37.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.31,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, the rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.78,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:39.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, get in! Kouhai-kun, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:42.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.70,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, taxi! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.30,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka! Don't try to cop \Na feel in the chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.13,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But where there are boobs, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.62,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about them \Nlike they're mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I can make it the \Nrest of the way myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.15,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san?! We've been \Nlooking for you! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to a cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami was exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd only get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We left the house in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should buy an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.49,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go buy it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:17.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! With everything that's been \Ngoing on, I forgot it was out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care much about release dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.20,Sign,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,Nanohana Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Look. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I already know the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.99,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Well done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.45,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.31,Saku-main,STUDNETS,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sprint to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.41,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:14:59.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.17,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.75,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much trouble \Nyou caused everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:07.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.38,Saku-main,MOMOKO,0000,0000,0000,,If it was going to turn out like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.72,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have just stayed home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,After you went through the \Ntrouble to bring me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced so hard for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I let it all go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:53.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst... I'm despicable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you told me that I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was pushing myself too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I took so much upon myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,thinking I could do a better job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I was just being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you ignore what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Smile and tell me I'm \Njust a stupid little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't... if you don't, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:26.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're stupid, that makes \Nthe whole world stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? \NDon't be so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:34.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin was pushing herself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's hard on others and herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:11.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least, she always tries to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:15.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand why \Nyou said your impression of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.39,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she was always fighting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents' opposition, \Nor maybe her own nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she couldn't rely on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If she gave in to weakness even once,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she thought she'd end up \Ngiving in again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what made her stubborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and made her put pressure on herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.82,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you finally understand that, \Nthat may be its own reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.08,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mashiro-chan still with Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she has her own \Nfeelings on the matter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.47,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Samgyetang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured a special hotpot would \Nbe appropriate for this occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Special"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nanamin showed us weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, samgyetang isn't \Nthe same as hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you sweat the details,\N you'll never be a chick magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Torajiro. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.05,Saku-main,TORA,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but what happened \Nyesterday was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They saw me crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I know I had a fever, \Nbut I couldn't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.48,Saku-main,TORA,0000,0000,0000,,You clung to him the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:55.28,Saku-main,TORA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a tease. \NGo for it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,T-Torajiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's Torajiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't you knock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I did. Besides, it was already open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:10.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were the \Ntype to talk to pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.72,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't take \Nthe bowl in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:25.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry, it'll get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:52.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She held my hand all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Shiina understood \Nyou better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:01.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If Shiina hadn't said anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have stopped you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She said if it were her, she'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,And to take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She begged us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been \Nwatching you work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't gone, I would \Nhave regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at Shiina-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize I still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:32.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She stays up late every \Nnight working on her manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She redraws it over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed talented people \Ndidn't have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:45.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How can I catch up to that kind of talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Catch up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,At Shiina-san's sleeping face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look around the room, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Or at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,And don't get too close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That kinda hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,...because I haven't bathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I said the samgyetang tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:15.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,About Mashiro Duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:23.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but honestly, I don't \Nthink I can keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:30.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Thanks for relying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm the one who \Nshould be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:34.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to call \Nme by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:47.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shii— Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on Mashiro Duty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:22:00.77,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Mashiro Duty has passed from Aoyama Nanami\N back to Kanda Sorata. -By Kanda Sorata\N\NP.S. - Kanda-kun, I'm sorry for everything. \NI forgot to tell you something, so I'm writing \Nit here. If you do anything weird to Mashiro,\N I'll never forgive you! -Aoyama Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:55.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will wake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wake up, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:00.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:16.04,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda: Mashiro Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.04,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:17.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Dry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,#07 Her Homesickness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:38.33,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko is coming.
